---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../../styles/globals.css";
import { Header } from "../../components/Header";
import InnerPageCTA from "../../components/InnerPageCTA.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";

const b = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout
  title="How to Improve On-Time Delivery - parcelLab"
  description="On-time delivery is a critical KPI for ecommerce success. This guide explains actionable strategies to improve delivery rates consistently."
>
  <Header client:load />
  <main>
    <section class="section-generous">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1440px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px]">
          <a href={`${b}/blog/`} class="group mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--ink-muted)] transition-colors hover:text-[#3D3AD3]">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="transition-transform group-hover:-translate-x-0.5"><path d="M19 12H5"/><path d="m12 19-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
            Back to blog
          </a>
          <span class="mb-4 inline-block rounded-full bg-[#3D3AD3]/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-[#3D3AD3]">Delivery Experience</span>
          <h1 class="text-display text-[var(--ink)]">How to Improve On-Time Delivery</h1>
          <div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">
            <span>By <strong class="font-medium text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">Anna Lapezo</strong></span>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <time datetime="2023-10-05">October 5, 2023</time>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <span>8 min read</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pb-16 md:pb-24">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed text-lg">
          On-time delivery is a KPI that shows how well and how often a company meets its delivery promises. A good OTD percentage to aim for is 95% or above. Research shows that 53% of consumers view the post-purchase stage as the most emotional part of their shopping journey.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">Why Is On-Time Delivery So Important?</h2>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#035740" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]"><strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">Improved customer satisfaction</strong> and higher levels of trust</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#035740" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]"><strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">More repeat purchases</strong> and strong competitive advantage</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#035740" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]"><strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">Fewer returns</strong> and reduced operational costs</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">How to Improve On-Time Delivery</h2>
        <ol class="mt-4 space-y-3 list-decimal list-inside">
          <li class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">Forecast demand and optimize inventory management</strong></li>
          <li class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">Streamline your warehouse operations</strong></li>
          <li class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">Opt for less packaging if possible</strong></li>
          <li class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">Choose the right logistics and delivery partners</strong></li>
          <li class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">Keep your systems tightly integrated</strong></li>
          <li class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">Use data to determine optimal delivery times</strong></li>
        </ol>

        <div class="my-10 rounded-2xl bg-[var(--surface-sunken)] p-8">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-[var(--ink-muted)]">Case Study</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">GRANIT Parts leverages parcelLab to provide proactive communication during delays, resulting in <strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">20% fewer inquiry calls</strong> and <strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">15% fewer inquiry emails</strong>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <InnerPageCTA />
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
